{"id": 2891, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对购物休闲的“第三空间”都有哪些基本要求？", "description": "住哪看预算成本，在哪工作看公司要求，剩下的第三空间，你有啥偏好吗？（题图来自：istock ©️ lankogal）", "record_count": 2110, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190409110534LU4FtkQnNsXzahZm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 338690, "content": "小便池隐私好一点儿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 338696, "content": "贵点无所谓，环境摆第一", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 837977}, {"id": 338698, "content": "卫生间的每一格不要空间太挤", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882331}, {"id": 339211, "content": "没人吸烟，厕所方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617819}, {"id": 338700, "content": "卫生间干净，这在小城市尤其难以做到。人有三急，服务自然要先从紧上来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633922}, {"id": 338701, "content": "可以有喝水的地方，类似扫码自助这种。对于一个很渴的人来说，没水还不想排队喝奶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1625867}, {"id": 338702, "content": "出租车里没有陈年的味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498217}, {"id": 338704, "content": "安静 不喜欢很吵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052680}, {"id": 338705, "content": "住房必定要交通方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633378}, {"id": 338706, "content": "休息区舒适", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615113}, {"id": 338714, "content": "座位舒服点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276287}, {"id": 338715, "content": "一个人不会显得突兀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519185}, {"id": 338717, "content": "卫生间干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635123}, {"id": 339229, "content": "洗手间干净无味。有沙发或者椅子可以坐下来休息。没有噪音污染。", "image": "img/option/option/20190414211707tiU3lwkZoInm97RY.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637868}, {"id": 338721, "content": "导购不要跟着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630983}, {"id": 339233, "content": "空气要好  No somking", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637916}, {"id": 338727, "content": "附近有一个花店、安静的咖啡厅、健身馆～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635196}, {"id": 339496, "content": "最好不要有人盯着，服务态度再好，也不太舒服…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635348}, {"id": 338731, "content": "不用再为工作烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635221}, {"id": 338732, "content": "能安静地享受购物，环境舒适", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635231}, {"id": 339247, "content": "可以充电，厕所干净。有些生活情趣之类的比如电影安利这样好感度就会多很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576910}, {"id": 338737, "content": "没有人吸烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}, {"id": 338738, "content": "可以满足陌生人社交", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819308}, {"id": 338739, "content": "卫生间不要都是马桶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635396}, {"id": 338740, "content": "一个不太可能达到的要求：安静。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1324195}, {"id": 338741, "content": "一个24小时安静的书店", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814270}, {"id": 338742, "content": "没有很拥挤，环境也不用太奢华，干净整洁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1575996}, {"id": 338771, "content": "服务周到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635040}, {"id": 338773, "content": "卫生间有手纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635040}, {"id": 339036, "content": "有可以存放衣服物品的地方！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1461564}, {"id": 338796, "content": "可以携带宠物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080877}, {"id": 339588, "content": "洗手间高档", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1628720}, {"id": 338567, "content": "停车方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 868692}, {"id": 338568, "content": "洗手间干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 547, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1584734}, {"id": 338570, "content": "买的东西可以不用一直提着", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597047}, {"id": 338572, "content": "不想因为一个人吃饭，捧着餐盘找座位。", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634582}, {"id": 338574, "content": "卫生间好找", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 338579, "content": "可以充电，不会有人一直四处看，都在闲聊，气氛不会过于凝重，不会经常有服务生过来推荐东西也不会经常问我是否可以把东西收走", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632811}, {"id": 338580, "content": "可以充电，不会有人一直四处看，都在闲聊，气氛不会过于凝重，不会经常有服务生过来推荐东西也不会经常问我是否可以把东西收走", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632811}, {"id": 338582, "content": "别有人一直盯着我", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1515036}, {"id": 338583, "content": "我还挺幻想期待禁言商场的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 338584, "content": "不用拼桌", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1585971}, {"id": 338586, "content": "没有过于热情的导购", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485754}, {"id": 338587, "content": "隐形人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1618559}, {"id": 338588, "content": "没有熊孩子", "image": null, "praise_count":